    "By optimizing the design of prompt, users can better guide models to produce outputs that meet their specific needs.",
    "We try to provide some reference content as follows:• Define the task or objective.",
    "Clearly specify the task or objective you want the model to accomplish.",
    "This could be answering questions, generating articles,etc.",
    "• Understand the model's capabilities."
